The ExtractCount() sequentially applies rule-specific conversions before applying CogComp Quantifier to achieve maximum recall. The function first applying type conversion (int(``17''){{arxiv_2209_07250_FO0008||FO}}17, float(``17.0''){{arxiv_2209_07250_FO0009||FO}}17.0), followed by a dictionary based look-up for worded to integer conversion (``seventeen''{{arxiv_2209_07250_FO0010||FO}}17) and lastly the CogComp Quantifier, proceeding only when the previous conversion yields empty results. The counts are further cleaned by removing fractions {{arxiv_2209_07250_FO0011||FO}}, since counts are whole numbers.